{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were on that train 13 days, just circling around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because at this time now, it was-- the end of the war was coming close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the Americans and the British were coming from the west.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "The Russians were coming from the east, and the train could not go through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we got nothing to eat on the train, and the train would stop, sometimes for days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we would go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we would have been able to escape, but we never thought of, of escaping.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This is how we had lost the ability to plan, to reason.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We just always went back to the, to the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I remember one time, we were in the middle of a forest, and it was so beautiful, so green.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there was a sparkling brook that was just rushing through the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And it just-- you know, it was like a reawakening, a rebirth, spring time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And it felt so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But we always went back, and we just drank whatever puddles there were on the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I don't know what we ate, because I don't remember eating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But one morning we woke up, and we heard people shouting outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We are free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And nobody paid much attention to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "But then, we looked outside and we saw Russian soldiers taking the German guards, the few German guards who were still on the train, prisoners.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we knew that the Russians had overtaken the, the area and had seized the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Most of the Germans already had fled the train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And then, the Russians didn't know what to make of us, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But they looked inside, and then they realized who we were.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
